# Highlight Armour by Defence Type

Show
    Class == "Body Armours" "Boots" "Gloves" "Helmets" "Shields"
    Rarity Rare
    SetBackgroundColor 0 0 0 168
    SetFontSize 42
    SetTextColor 255 255 0 255
    SetBorderColor 255 255 0 255
